2:T75e,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Kapwing AI better than Pictory?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Kapwing AI scores 6.0 overall while Pictory scores 6.0. Kapwing AI is best for content teams collaborating on video and quick social media edits, while Pictory excels for marketers repurposing long-form content and social media clips."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Kapwing AI or Pictory?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Kapwing AI starts at $16/mo and Pictory starts at $19/mo. Kapwing AI offers a free plan. Pictory offers a free plan. Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Kapwing AI to Pictory?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Kapwing AI and Pictory support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Kapwing AI vs Pictory?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Kapwing AI holds an overall rating of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10. Pictory has an overall rating of 6/10 and ease of use score of 8/10. Users praise Kapwing AI for browser-based, no install and Pictory for great long-to-short conversion."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Kapwing AI or Pictory?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Pictory for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Kapwing AI remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize browser-based, no install. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"oWPZTPCPUwZMl312gxRMA","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"applicat