7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Kapwing AI and Pictory share a solid foundation of core features including Auto Captions, Templates, Batch Processing. On the other hand, Pictory uniquely offers Text To Video and Stock Footage and Voice Over, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Kapwing AI holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10, while Pictory scores 6/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Kapwing AI offers a more budget-friendly entry point at $16/mo, compared to Pictory's starting price of $19/mo. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Kapwing AI's free tier and Pictory's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
